---
const quotes = [
  "Amazing app, native, simple, does what you want it to do, does not disturb you with useless features.",
  "Bleep is a simple & straightforward way to organize our messy thoughts, while keeping a trail of those moments we cherish dearly.",
  "Awesome app with very clean & beautiful interface. I'm so happy I found this!",
  "I'm a product designer, and I usually go around collecting notes, references, links to interesting things. Bleep has allowed me to organize myself better.",
  "No useless features or AI stuff â€” just my links, screenshots, and notes in a sleek, easy-to-use interface that keeps improving. Exactly what I was looking for!",
];
---

<section class="testimonials">
  <div class="testimonials-inner">
    {quotes.map((quote) => (
      <blockquote>&ldquo;{quote}&rdquo;</blockquote>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 5rem var(--safe-area-padding);
  }

  .testimonials-inner {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    columns: 1;
    column-gap: 3rem;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-family: "Jugendreisen", serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
    text-align: center;
    break-inside: avoid;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  blockquote:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  blockquote::before {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials {
      padding: 6rem var(--safe-area-padding);
    }

    .testimonials-inner {
      columns: 2;
    }

    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .testimonials {
      background: #111;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }
  }
</style>
